These are Puzzles for 4x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-2-1::.
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: april, march, july, october, january, august, november
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: rose, amaryllis, bellflower, marigold, balloon-flower, iris, lily
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: baseball, basketball, cricket, golf, skateboarding, surfing, swimming
The people use 7 different means of transport: bike, jet-ski, quad-bike, ship, subway, train, van
 1. the person who's sport is golf is on the far right##1
 2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the person who growsmarigold##1
 3. the person driving the subway is the person who's sport is cricket##1
 4. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the person driving the train##1
 5. the person who growsrose is on the right of the person who growslily##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in march is the person who's sport is cricket##1
 7. the person driving the van is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
 8. the person driving the ship is between the person driving the van and the person who growsiris##2
 9. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
10. the person who's birthday is in july is in the middle##1
11. the person who's sport is baseball is the person who's birthday is in january##1
12. the person who's birthday is in january is the person driving the bike##1
13. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person who growsbellflower##1
14. the person who growsiris is the person driving the quad-bike##1
15. the person driving the train is on the left of the person who growslily##1
16. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
17. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person who growsbellflower##1
18. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
19. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |    3     |     4      |     5     |    6     |    7    |
| Birthday      | march  | august        | january | july      | october     | april      | november     |
| Flower   | amaryllis | marigold         | lily   | rose | iris    | balloon-flower | bellflower |
| Sport         | cricket | skateboarding | baseball | basketball | swimming  | surfing  | golf    |
| Transport     | subway  | train         | bike     | jet-ski    | quad-bike | ship     | van     |

