.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-2-2::.
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: lacrosse, sailing, volleyball, tennis, water-polo, snowboarding, rugby
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, baccarat, siglo, chaman, cain, fonseca, dunhill
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: ambient, disco, indie, metal, pop, reggae, rock
The people use 7 different means of transport: boat, car, helicopter, quad-bike, roller, ship, skateboard
 1. the person who's sport is sailing is the chaman-smoker##1
 2. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the cain-smoker##1
 3. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
 4. the baccarat-smoker is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
 5. the person driving the ship is on the right of the siglo-smoker##1
 6. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
 7. the fonseca-smoker is the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
 8. the fan of rock is the person driving the skateboard##1
 9. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
10. the fan of metal is between the fan of indie and the dunhill-smoker##2
11. the fan of disco is the chaman-smoker##1
12. the fan of pop is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
13. the fan of pop is between the dunhill-smoker and the fan of reggae##2
14. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
15. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person driving the car##1
16. the person driving the skateboard is on the far left##1
17. the bongani-smoker is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
18. the baccarat-smoker is on the left of the siglo-smoker##1
19. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
20. the siglo-smoker is between the person driving the ship and the baccarat-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |    3     |     4      |    5    |     6      |     7     |
| Sport      | water-polo   | volleyball | lacrosse      | tennis   | rugby     | snowboarding    | sailing      |
| Cigar          | bongani    | baccarat     | siglo | dunhill | cain | fonseca  | chaman |
