The people have 7 different hobbies: board-games, filmmaking, hiking, reading, rock-climbing, sudoku, traveling
House: townhouse, cottage, futuristic, gothic-revival, farmhouse, colonial, craftsman
City: venice, hannover, new-york, edinburgh, miami, colone, hamburg
 1. the person traveling to colone is the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 2. the person traveling to miami is on the right of the cottage house##1
 3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the far left##1
 4. the person traveling to venice is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
 5. the person drinking lemonade is on the far left##1
 6. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
 7. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
 8. the person drinking mirinda is in the middle##1
 9. the person drinking sprite is the person traveling to colone##1
10. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the person traveling to colone##1
11. the person traveling to edinburgh is the colonial house##1
12. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person who's hobby is reading##1
13. the cottage house is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
14. the futuristic house is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
15. the person drinking tea is on the right of the craftsman house##1
16. the person who's hobby is reading is the futuristic house##1
17. the person traveling to venice is on the left of the townhouse house##1
18. the person traveling to new-york is between the person traveling to miami and the person traveling to hannover##2
19. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2      |     3     |      4       |       5        |      6      |      7      |
